song.title: Skip
song.info:
Made in cooperation with [url=http://www.mantraporno.hu/]Mantraporno[/url] for Breakpoint 2008.
[i]Lyrics: Fly to me this way is leading down. Help me now although I need some time. Half asleep I forgot all about you But yet I'm here So tell the truth of your history.
Fly away and then dream again see your face count your days
Life is blue, but your hopes are always bright Dark is night, but you bring me all the lights[/i]
Included in "BitJam Podcast Episode #110 - Sexiest Female Singers Part 2", Track 13
